             were indicted for <rs id="t18230625-36-off218" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230625-36-off218" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230625-36-off218" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230625-36-cd219" type="crimeDate">3d of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-36-off218 t18230625-36-cd219"></join>, a handkerchief, value 3 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230625-36-victim371" type="victimName">
                           Clement 
                           Harris
                        <interp inst="t18230625-36-victim371" type="surname" value="Harris"></interp>
